This is simple and sublime! At my supermarket, I can buy Indian ghee (clarified butter) in a jar, so I have it for many purposes whenever I need it. This is just a regular store, not an ethnic market, so if you can find ghee you have your clarified butter. Ask your grocer. We have a weakness for soft-shell crabs, but this recipe gets an A+ for both flavor and simplicity. It's a 10 in my book!

